                            Referrals provided for daily living such as pet care, home repair, errand services, travel, entertainment and apartment locator services.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading lu" role="tab" id="headingEight">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEight">
                                Wellness Referrals
                            </a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseEight" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingEight">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            Help with physician searches, medical support groups, fitness centers, diet & nutrition resources, alternative medicine and other resources.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading lu" role="tab" id="headingNine">
                        <h4 class="panel-title">
                            <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNine">
                                Claremont Personal Advantage(CPA)
                            </a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseNine" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingNine">
                        <div class="panel-body">
                            Unlimited access is provided to Claremont’s Enhanced Web Site for articles, resources, videos and assessments about health, finance, legal issues, personal growth, stress, family life and more.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>For more information, go to <a href="http://www.claremonteap.com/pages/cap.html" />http://claremonteap.com</a> and use company name: Local 831</br></br>Extended eligibility for Substance Abuse Counseling and Treatment is available solely to the employee for 6 months after the loss of eligibility for coverage. </p>

